<div style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 1.3em;">
How to start:
</div>
<ol>
  <li> On your mobile device:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0;">
      <li> login at <a href="http://jdrop.org/">http://jdrop.org/</a>
      <li> install any of the <a href="apps">apps</a> that use JDrop
      <li> run the app and save data to JDrop
    </ul>
  <li> On your desktop or laptop:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0;">
      <li> login at <a href="http://jdrop.org/">http://jdrop.org/</a> using the same "username" you used on the mobile device
      <li> view the <a href="myjson">JSON data</a> that you generated
    </ul>
</ol>



<p style="margin-top: 40px;">
Checkout the <a href="example">example use case</a> for screenshots and more information.
</p>


